    abstract class AbstractAnimation<T extends Key,D extends IsDefaultBaseAnimation>
extends AbstractNode
implements IsDefaultBaseAnimation, HasCallbackScope
    Is the base animation options with common options for animation configuration, for ANIMATION and ANIMATIONS name spaces.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
